<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="speak-vi">speak <strong><em>vi</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /spiːk/    美 /spiːk/  </p>
<p>(spoke, spoken)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>说话；讲 (话)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>speak in English
用英语说</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please speak more slowly to make your speech understood.
为了让别人听懂你的演讲，请说得再慢些。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>谈话；交谈：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ll <strong>speak to</strong> the hospital management about that.
我会向医院管理人员反映那个情况。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Can I <strong>speak with</strong> Tom, please?
请问，我能和汤姆通话吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Speaking.
我就是，请讲。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>演讲；发言：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>speak on global warming
就全球气候变暖进行演讲</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— Can I speak to Mr Wang, please?
— <strong><em>_</em></strong><strong><em>_</em></strong>.  （2005 全国）<br />
A.Who are you?<br />
B.I’m Wang.<br />
C.Speaking.<br />
D.Are you John?  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. C  </p></div>